value.title: Pastor Greg Locke Says Only 'Crack-Smoking' Leftists Believe Joe Biden Won Election
value.excerpt: Controversial Tennessee pastor Greg Locke again insisted President Joe Biden was not legitimately elected, and claimed only "crack-smoking" leftists would think he beat Donald Trump to the White House.
